
1  

Kipou keboikinos kwap kariri naka icorin luka Babulon, Eebo, kipou kamonyata akiyo kanen,

Nakiitunio Sion.


2  Kipou kekajakisi akosideudeun

Okito lukanen.


3  Naarai akotosi lukiŋatarito sio ikososio kamakosi,

Ŋul da lukimwanito sio akotosi aboliasio, kobalas ebe, “Koyeikinai sio ediopet kokososio luka Sion.”


4  Kiyei isio biai ekosio loka EJAKAIT Kacekwap?


5  Arai keemurwoki ijo, wu Yerusalem,

Kimurwoki da akakan nakoteten apirianutuke.


6  

Kiminaikin do akaŋajep aŋiirit naka aitukuka,

Arai mam keitunit jo;

Arai mam etopoloorit Yerusalem

Adepar akaiyalama kere.


7  

Wu EJAKAIT, kiitu aluikin idwe luka Edom,

Kanuka apaaran naka Yerusalem;

Luabalas ebe, “Kotiyaikisi, kotiyaikisi,

Kiton apetetaitike.”


8  

Wu apese naka Babulon, kimudiario jo:

Iyalamikini ŋesi yenikiropi jo

Kwape kiswamakinia sio.


9  Iyatamikini ŋesi, yenedakuni kosodi aideeakin

Ludidikikon atiiba.

